						               													<description>Hat-Trick: 'Players' Expansion, the first expansion for the card-driven soccer simulation Hat-Trick, includes rules and components for the following:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     22 player roles &amp;ndash; from now on you will be able to customize your line-up by assigning roles like Playmaker, False no. 9, Wingback, etc. to your players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     44 player skills &amp;ndash; each of the 22 player roles has 2 unique skills - a stronger and weaker one. Depending which side a given player is on, he will be able to use one of these skills.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     45 unique national teams &amp;ndash; by means of the new system, the game recreates 45 national teams, each with different strength, line-up and playing style.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     12 style cards &amp;ndash; from now on each team will have an assigned playing style &amp;ndash; technical, tactical, physical or total &amp;ndash; and, thus, will be able to use the corresponding Style Cards to perform style-unique plays.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     6 match events &amp;ndash; the expansion introduces 6 match events like corners or substitutions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     3 budget cards &amp;ndash; the Budget Cards make it possible to customize teams of different mentality (attacking, balanced, defensive) and affluence. This way you will be able to recreate any team in the world.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
